*Prodaju* se nove proizvode. (They are selling new products.)

*Prodaju* se i starija vozila. (They are also selling older vehicles.)

Na internetu se *prodaju* veoma jeftini proizvodi. (Very cheap products are being sold on the internet.)

Neke firme *prodaju* svoje proizvode po cenama koje su mnogo niže od tržišne. (Some companies are selling their products at prices much lower than the market.)

Neki ljudi *prodaju* polovne stvari na internetu. (Some people are selling second-hand items online.)

*Prodaju* se i domaći proizvodi. (Domestic products are also being sold.)